==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: The plans of man cannot compare to the plans of heaven. 

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: rén sùan bù rú tīan sùan

===Idiom===
'''[[人]][[算]][[不]][[如]][[天]][[算]]'''

# No matter how much one plans things out, life always intervenes.

